        "title": "",
        "html": "<h2>High-Quality Workwear at Unbeatable Prices</h2>\n\n<p>Our Clearance Collection is filled with premium workwear that offers the same trusted durability and comfort you expect from DNC Direct, but at a fraction of the regular price. Whether you’re looking to replace worn-out gear or add to your existing collection, this is the perfect opportunity to get more for less. Every item in this collection has been carefully selected to ensure it meets our high standards, so you can shop with confidence knowing you’re getting the best value.</p>\n\n<h2>Why Shop Our Clearance Collection?</h2>\n\n<p>The Clearance Collection is ideal for those who want top-quality workwear without the premium price tag. Each product is built to withstand tough work environments while providing the comfort and protection you need. With a wide range of sizes and styles available, there’s something for everyone. These deals won’t last forever, so act fast to secure the best prices on workwear that’s built to last.</p>\n\n<h2>Features and Benefits</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Significant Savings:</strong> Enjoy deep discounts on high-quality workwear, including jackets, shirts, trousers, and boots.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Durable Construction:</strong> All items are made from premium materials designed to withstand the rigours of demanding work environments.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Comfortable Fit:</strong> Each piece is crafted with comfort in mind, ensuring you can work all day without discomfort.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Wide Range of Sizes:</strong> Our Clearance Collection includes a variety of sizes, so you’re sure to find the perfect fit.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Trusted Australian Brand:</strong> Shop with confidence from a brand that’s 100% Australian owned and operated.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<span id=\"dots\">...</span><span id=\"more\">\n\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Q: What types of products are included in the Clearance Collection?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Our Clearance Collection features a variety of workwear items, including jackets, shirts, trousers, boots, and more, all at significantly reduced prices.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: Are these items of the same quality as your regular products?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Yes, all items in our Clearance Collection meet the same high standards of quality and durability as our regular-priced products.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: How long will the items in the Clearance Collection be available?</strong></p>\n<p>A: The Clearance Collection features limited-time offers, so we recommend shopping early to secure the best deals before they sell out.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: Are there different sizes available in the Clearance Collection?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Yes, we offer a wide range of sizes to ensure you find the perfect fit. Please refer to our size guide for detailed measurements.</p>\n\n<p>From time to time we like to make way for new and exciting things and so we will end of line certain items. As these items have limited quantity available then it's unlikely you'll be able to buy 5 and get the 20% discount however they will count if you buy other things</p>\n\n<p>These will be dispatched to you from a different warehouse so will come in a separate package (don't worry you don't have to pay extra postage!</p>\n\n</span>\n\n<strong><button onclick=\"myFunction()\" id=\"myBtn\">Read more</button></strong>\n\n<style>\n#more {display: none;}\n</style>\n\n\n<script>\nfunction myFunction() {\n  var dots = document.getElementById(\"dots\");\n  var moreText = document.getElementById(\"more\");\n  var btnText = document.getElementById(\"myBtn\");\n\n  if (dots.style.display === \"none\") {\n    dots.style.display = \"inline\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read more\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"none\";\n  } else {\n    dots.style.display = \"none\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read less\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"inline\";\n  }\n}\n</script>"
      }
